|receiver.firstname|,

I'm sorry. It won't happen again, I swear. To tell the truth, things have been tough at home and I know it has been affecting my work. But I swear I'll do better from now on. 

I'll work overtime to catch up; please give me a few weeks to prove myself. 

Thank you in advance.

Budu pracovat prescas, abych to dohnal; prosim, dejte mi par tydnu, abych se osvedcil.

You have twenty-four (24) hours to clear your possessions and deliver the key to the building supervisor, or action will be taken against you. Failure to comply will result in your immediate physical removal from the property by enforcers. \r\n\r\n Any monies owing will be recovered in due course, plus a penalty for any damage to the property.

TENANCY AGREEMENT

Drawn up between the the Landlord |owner.landlord.fullname| and the Tenant |owner.fullname|. 

Relating to the rental of apartment |owner.home.name|.

This tenancy agreement is subject to the regulations of the Joint Corporation Housing Consortium (J.C.H.C.) A copy of these regulations may be obtained in writing from the nearest J.C.H.C Administration Bureau on receipt of a processing fee. 

The notice period will be one week on the side of the Landlord and two months on the side of the Tenant. The key must be delivered to the Administration Bureau by 12 noon on the day of expiry. Financial penalties shall be incurred for every additional 30 minutes.

All broken windows, locks, lamps, sockets, sprockets, outlets, inlets, pipes, faucets, vents, grills and appliances must be repaired or replaced by the Tenant. 

The Tenant shall not repair or replace any windows, locks, lamps, sockets, sprockets, outlets, inlets, pipes, faucets, vents, grills, drawers and appliances without express permission of the Landlord.

The Tenant shall keep in good repair all walls, tiles and flooring. 

The Tenant shall not paint, plaster, paper or alter walls, tiles or flooring in any way. 

The Tenant shall not encourage nor harbour pigeons, rodents or microscopic life forms of any kind and shall call pest control upon first sighting. 

The Tenant shall not sublet any rooms or floor space. 

The Tenant shall not dry laundry upon fire escapes or from windowsills. Visible laundry will incur a penalty from the Building Supervisor. 

Nails are not to be driven into the walls. Wiring is not to be tampered with. 

The garbage bin is for DRY trash only. Any organic matter or waste fluids must be disposed of using the communal garbage chute. Any organic trash matter found in the premises will incur a financial penalty. 

The Tenant shall not cultivate moss, mildew or mould for any purpose including nutrition or recreation. More than one (1) patch of living matter will incur a financial penalty. 

Any change in employment MUST be reported IMMEDIATELY. Failure to notify the Landlord or Bureau within twenty-four (24) hours will result in immediate eviction. 

The Tenant shall not keep any explosives in or on the property. 

The Tenant shall not display or affix any visual media relating to a rival corporation to any surface. Any such media will be removed and destroyed without warning and a financial penalty will be incurred. 

The Tenant shall collect all mail promptly. Mail left unattended for more than 48 hours will be held by the Building Supervisor and returned upon payment of a late fee. Any mail uncollected after seven (7) days will be destroyed. 

The Landlord, any staff member of the J.C.H.C or the Building Supervisor shall be at liberty to enter the dwelling for any reason at any time without prior notice. 

The Tenant agrees not to shower or perform ablutions under running water for more than fifteen (15) minutes. 

The Tenant agrees not to allow the premises to be used for illegal activities including prostitution, gambling or brewing. 

Visitors must be registered with the Landlord and Building Supervisor in advance. 

The Tenant agrees not to wear stiletto or noise-making shoes in communal areas. 

Any breach of the above terms, plus further terms to be found in the General Regulations, shall result in immediate eviction.
Displayed Text:
NAJEMNI SMLOUVA

Sepsana mezi pronajimatelem |owner.landlord.fullname| a najemcem |owner.fullname|. 

O pronajmu bytu |owner.home.name|.

Tato najemni smlouva podleha predpisum Spolecneho bytoveho konsorcia (J.C.H.C.) Kopii techto predpisu lze ziskat pisemne na nejblizsi spravni kancelari J.C.H.C. po zaplaceni poplatku za zpracovani. 

Vypovedni lhuta cini jeden tyden na strane pronajimatele a dva mesice na strane najemce. Klic musi byt dorucen do spravni kancelare do 12 hodin v den ukonceni platnosti vypovedi. Za kazdych dalsich 30 minut hrozi financni sankce.

Vsechna rozbita okna, zamky, lampy, zasuvky, hvezdice, zasuvky, privody, potrubi, kohoutky, ventilacni otvory, mrize a spotrebice musi opravit nebo vymenit najemce. 
Najemce nesmi bez vyslovneho souhlasu pronajimatele opravovat nebo vymenovat okna, zamky, svitidla, zasuvky, hvezdice, zasuvky, privody, potrubi, baterie, ventilacni otvory, mrizky, zasuvky a spotrebice.

Najemce musi udrzovat v dobrem stavu vsechny steny, obklady a podlahy. 

Najemce nesmi malovat, omitat, lepit ani jakkoli upravovat steny, obklady nebo podlahu. 

Najemce nesmi podporovat ani prechovavat holuby, hlodavce nebo mikroskopicke formy zivota jakehokoli druhu a musi pri prvnim spatreni zavolat kontrolu skudcu. 

Najemce nesmi pronajimat zadne mistnosti ani podlahovou plochu. 

Najemce nesmi susit pradlo na pozarnich schodech nebo na okennich parapetech. Za viditelne pradlo hrozi spravci budovy pokuta. 

Na stenach nesmi byt zatloukany hrebiky. Do elektroinstalace se nesmi zasahovat. 

Kos na odpadky je urcen pouze pro SUCHE odpadky. Veskere organicke latky nebo odpadni tekutiny musi byt likvidovany pomoci spolecneho odpadkoveho zlabu. Jakekoli organicke odpadky nalezene v prostorach budou financne sankcionovany. 

Najemce nesmi pestovat mech, plisne nebo houby za zadnym ucelem, vcetne vyzivy nebo rekreace. Za vice nez jednu (1) skvrnu zive hmoty bude ulozena financni pokuta. 

Jakoukoli zmenu zamestnani MUSI najemce neprodlene nahlasit. Neoznameni pronajimateli nebo uradu do dvaceti ctyr (24) hodin bude mit za nasledek okamzite vystehovani. 

Najemce nesmi v objektu ani na nem prechovavat zadne vybusniny. 

Najemce nesmi na zadnem povrchu vystavovat ani pripevnovat zadne vizualni nosice tykajici se konkurencni spolecnosti. Jakakoli takova media budou bez varovani odstranena a znicena a bude ulozena financni pokuta. 

Najemce je povinen neprodlene prebirat veskerou postu. Posta ponechana bez dozoru dele nez 48 hodin bude zadrzena spravcem budovy a vracena po zaplaceni poplatku z prodleni. Posta nevyzvednuta po sedmi (7) dnech bude znicena. 

Pronajimatel, kterykoli zamestnanec J.C.H.C. nebo spravce budovy mohou kdykoli a bez predchoziho upozorneni vstoupit do obydli z jakehokoli duvodu. 

Najemce se zavazuje, ze se nebude sprchovat nebo myt pod tekouci vodou dele nez patnact (15) minut. 

Najemce se zavazuje, ze nedovoli, aby byly prostory vyuzivany k nezakonnym cinnostem vcetne prostituce, hazardnich her nebo vareni piva. 

Navstevnici musi byt predem zaregistrovani u pronajimatele a spravce budovy. 

Najemce se zavazuje, ze ve spolecnych prostorach nebude nosit obuv na jehlovem podpatku nebo obuv zpusobujici hluk. 

Jakekoli poruseni vyse uvedenych podminek a dalsich podminek, ktere jsou uvedeny v Obecnych pravidlech, bude mit za nasledek okamzite vystehovani.

Notes:
|story.kidnapper.firstname| came by tonight. I started to make dinner for us both but I could tell something was wrong; |story.kidnapper.firstname| was acting strange, and when I asked what was up they just changed the subject. 

When I asked again they got angry and left, saying they would talk to me tomorrow at the diner instead. 

I know |story.kidnapper.heshe|'s hiding something. |story.kidnapper.heshe| swore to me that |story.kidnapper.heshe|'d changed, but I'm not a fool. I know |story.kidnapper.heshe|'s hanging around with that lowlife again. But how can I help if |story.kidnapper.heshe| won't trust me?

I just hope |story.kidnapper.heshe| talks to me about it, and that it isn't too late, this time.
Displayed Text:
|story.kidnapper.firstname| dnes vecer se zastavil. Zacal jsem nam obema pripravovat veceri, ale poznal jsem, ze neco neni v poradku; |story.kidnapper.firstname| se choval divne, a kdyz jsem se zeptal, co se deje, proste zmenil tema. 

Kdyz jsem se zeptal znovu, nastvali se a odesli s tim, ze si se mnou promluvi zitra v restauraci. 

Vim, ze |story.kidnapper.heshe| neco skryva. |Prisahal mi, ze se zmenil, ale ja nejsem blazen. Vim, ze se |story.kidnapper.heshe| zase poflakuje s tim podradnym clovekem. Ale jak mu muzu pomoct, kdyz mi |story.kidnapper.heshe| nechce verit?

Jen doufam, ze se mnou |story.kidnapper.heshe| o tom promluvi a ze tentokrat nebude pozde.

Notes:
EMPLOYMENT AGREEMENT – PRIVATE AND CONFIDENTIAL 

This Employment Agreement is made as of this 09/09/1976 by and between |story.partnerfullname| (“Employee”) and Elliot Genetics (“Employer”).

 1. Employer shall employ Employee as a Senior Research Geneticist on a full time basis under this Agreement. In this capacity, Employee shall have the following duties and undertake the following responsibilities: 

- Participate in, and further the research of REDACTED
- REDACTED the development of exploitable commercial applications of the REDACTED programme
- Undertake duties within the REDACTED and follow the instructions of the REDACTED as required
- Any other tasks, duties, roles or assignments that the Employer deems necessary.

2. The Employee's work for the Employer is STRICTLY CONFIDENTIAL in its entirety. 

The Employee undertakes not to disclose in any form, whether written or verbal, any information acquired as a result of their employment. Should the employee disclose any item of information, the Employer has to right to serve them with a Notice 647D, consisting of: 

- Immediate dismissal
- Enhanced interrogation procedures
- Private custodial detention of an unspecified duration
- Pecuniary sanctions including seizure any and all private property and holdings of next of kin
- Any other measures deemed suitable by the Disclosure and Disciplinary Committee

The Employee and their next of kin agree to waive any and all rights to legal council in the event of a Notice 647D.

The Employee and their next of kin agree to indemnify the Employer against any claim of physical or mental damage in the pursuit of the veracity of claims made under a Notice 647D.
Displayed Text:
PRACOVNI SMLOUVA - SOUKROMA A DUVERNA 

Tato pracovni smlouva je uzavrena dne 09.09.1976 mezi |story.partnerfullname| ('Zamestnanec') a spolecnosti Elliot Genetics ('Zamestnavatel').

 1. Zamestnavatel zamestnava Zamestnance na zaklade teto dohody jako vedouciho vyzkumneho genetika na plny uvazek. V teto funkci bude mit Zamestnanec nasledujici povinnosti a prevezme nasledujici odpovednost: 

podilet se na vyzkumu REDACTED a dale se podilet na vyvoji vyuzitelnych komercnich aplikaci programu REDACTED
- plnit ukoly v ramci REDACTED a ridit se podle potreby pokyny REDACTED
- plnit jakekoli dalsi ukoly, povinnosti, role nebo zadani, ktere zamestnavatel povazuje za nezbytne.

2. Prace zamestnance pro zamestnavatele je v celem rozsahu STRICTLY CONFIDENTIAL. 

Zamestnanec se zavazuje, ze v zadne forme, at uz pisemne nebo ustni, nezverejni zadne informace ziskane v ramci sveho zamestnani. Pokud zamestnanec prozradi jakoukoli informaci, ma zamestnavatel pravo dorucit mu oznameni 647D, ktere obsahuje: 

- Okamzite propusteni
- Zprisnene postupy vyslechu
- Soukroma vazba na dobu neurcitou
- Penezite sankce vcetne zabaveni veskereho soukromeho majetku a majetku nejblizsich pribuznych
- Jakakoli jina opatreni, ktera Vybor pro odhalovani a disciplinarni rizeni povazuje za vhodna

Zamestnanec a jeho nejblizsi pribuzni souhlasi s tim, ze se v pripade oznameni 647D vzdavaji veskerych prav na pravni radu.

Zamestnanec a jeho nejblizsi pribuzni souhlasi s tim, ze odskodni zamestnavatele za jakoukoli fyzickou nebo dusevni ujmu pri snaze o prokazani pravdivosti tvrzeni vznesenych na zaklade oznameni 647D.

Notes:
Genome Decay and Health Risks in Hybrid Synchronization Packages 

By Professor Sam Umeki 

Unofficial translation by |story.partner.fullname|

Abstract: 

Applications for genetic sequencing have come a long way from the first, tentative genome assembly attempts of Ackerman and Diouf back in the early 1970s. With the rise in popularity of privatized and unregulated gene therapy and DNA alteration programmes – such as Elliot Genetics Sequence 'Rejuvenation' treatments – have come new challenges.
Displayed Text:
Rozpad genomu a zdravotni rizika v hybridnich synchronizacnich baliccich 

Profesor Sam Umeki 

Neoficialni preklad |story.partner.fullname|

Abstrakt: 

Pouziti genetickeho sekvenovani urazilo od prvnich nejistych pokusu Ackermana a Dioufa o sestaveni genomu na pocatku 70. let minuleho stoleti dlouhou cestu. S narustem popularity privatizovane a neregulovane genove terapie a programu na upravu DNA - jako je napriklad lecba 'omlazeni' pomoci Elliot Genetics Sequence - prisly nove vyzvy.
Alternate Text: konkretne vysledny rozpad a ztrata genomu, ktere mohou postihnout soukromeho uzivatele v dusledku nadmerne expozice. Tento clanek se snazi tyto nove obavy resit analyzou toho mala udaju, ktere jsou k dispozici o praci spolecnosti Elliot Genetics, spolu s udaji ziskanymi z ruznych univerzitnich vyzkumnych iniciativ sponzorovanych programem Kaizen-6.

Notes:
Toxicological Report on Product YCx12 

Overview

YCx12 is packaged and sold under the name Paxadol. Several months ago, company officials were informed that new additives to the product were causing severe side-effects.

This report details the toxicological findings. 

Short Conclusion

YCx12 has the potential to induce moderate to severe side effects in consumers. These include (but are not limited to):

- headaches
- nausea
- cirrhosis
- mild psychosis
- insomnia

There is also some evidence to suggest that these side-effects are more severe in individuals who have undergone Re-Sequencing. 

The Quality Control department advise the use of a warning label on the product to avoid legal implications.
Displayed Text:
Toxikologicka zprava o pripravku YCx12 

Prehled

YCx12 je balen a prodavan pod nazvem Paxadol. Pred nekolika mesici byli predstavitele spolecnosti informovani, ze nove prisady do vyrobku zpusobuji zavazne vedlejsi ucinky.

Tato zprava podrobne popisuje toxikologicka zjisteni. 

Kratky zaver

YCx12 ma potencial vyvolat u spotrebitelu stredne zavazne az zavazne nezadouci ucinky. Mezi ne patri (mimo jine):

- bolesti hlavy
- nevolnost
- cirhoza
- mirna psychoza
- nespavost
Nektere dukazy take naznacuji, ze tyto nezadouci ucinky jsou zavaznejsi u jedincu, kteri podstoupili Re-Sequencing. 

Oddeleni kontroly kvality doporucuje pouzivat na pripravku varovne oznaceni, aby se predeslo pravnim dusledkum.

Monday, 11pm
This is supposed to help, the group leader said so. Dunno what I'm supposed to put down but |story.notewriter.casualname| said it sounded like a good idea. Everything sounds like a good idea when |story.notewriter.heshe| says it. 

Trying to cut down on Starch - not easy. 7 cans today.

Thursday, 9.45pm
Good day today. Went walking with |story.notewriter.casualname| down to the water. Even saw a bird. Felt like a normal nobody, on a normal afternoon. 

Cans of Starch = 5. Will do even better tomorrow. 

Friday, 1am
|story.associate.firstname| called. 

Should've known it wouldn't be this easy. Meeting tomorrow. 
Cans of Starch = 10. 

Tried to get out. Said I didn't want to do this anymore, that I was done. But |story.associate.firstname| just laughed, told me it was in my blood, like the Starch. 

Hope |story.notewriter.casualname| is safe. Shouldn't have told |story.notewriter.himher| anything, but they knew something was wrong and we said no secrets. Wish I'd kept my goddam mouth shut
 
|story.notewriter.heshe| won't pick up. Want to head over there, but |story.associate.firstname| might be watching. Makes me sick. No choice, got to

Notes: |casualname|

Dear |receiver.firstname|

Thanks for the letter. I am glad to hear you are doing well. As for us, I've not worked for 67 days and we'll be evicted again soon, I think. William has not been well and there ain't nothing helps but starch though the doc at the free clinic says its the starch did it in the first place. I think we might get lucky and get a floor space in one of the shelters.

I hate to ask and I know you hate it too but if you can send us even one crow it would help.
Displayed Text:
Vazeni |receiver.firstname|

Dekuji za dopis. Jsem rad, ze se ti dari dobre. Co se tyce nas, nepracuji uz 67 dni a myslim, ze nas brzy zase vystehuji. Williamovi neni dobre a nepomaha nic nez skrob, i kdyz doktor na bezplatne klinice rika, ze to zpusobil predevsim skrob. Myslim, ze budeme mit stesti a dostaneme misto v jednom z utulku.Nerada se ptam a vim, ze vy to taky nesnasite, ale kdybyste nam mohli poslat treba jen jednu vranu, pomohlo by to.

A Lazarus 5 semi automatic pistol. Produced in large numbers during the mustard war. Uses low calibre 8mm ammunition.
Displayed Text: Poloautomaticka pistole Lazarus 5. Vyrabela se ve velkem mnozstvi behem horcicne valky. Pouziva strelivo male raze 8 mm.

Notes: A silencer compatible with Lazarus pistols. Will make shots less audible.
Displayed Text: Tlumic kompatibilni s pistolemi Lazarus. Snizuje slysitelnost vystrelu.

Notes: A small box of 8mm pistol ammunition.
A box of 12-gauge shotgun shells.
A cup commonly used to hold hot drinks, often tea.
Displayed Text: Salek bezne pouzivany k uchovavani horkych napoju, casto caje.

Notes: A box of rifle rounds.
Sync disks contain DNA sequences that can be installed at a Sync Clinic for special abilities and upgrades.
Displayed Text: Sync disky obsahuji sekvence DNA, ktere lze nainstalovat na Klinika Sync a ziskat tak specialni schopnosti a vylepseni.

Notes: A cosmetic used to apply color or texture to the lips.
Displayed Text: Kosmeticky pripravek pouzivany k nanaseni barvy nebo textury na rty.

Notes: Stay up to date with current events in the city, or use it to conceal yourself from pursuers.
Displayed Text: Mejte prehled o aktualnim deni ve meste nebo se pomoci nej ukryjte pred pronasledovateli.

Notes: A crumpled sheet of paper with an unfinished drawing.
Displayed Text: Zmackany list papiru s nedokoncenou kresbou.

Notes: A crumpled sheet of paper.
An unwashed plate that has been used to hold food.
Displayed Text: Neumyty talir, na kterem bylo ulozeno jidlo.

Notes: A mug, commonly used to hold hot drinks, often tea.
Displayed Text: Hrnek, ktery se bezne pouziva k uchovavani horkych napoju, casto caje.

Notes: A clean plate.
A square paper napkin that has been used and crumpled into a ball.
Displayed Text: Ctvercovy papirovy ubrousek, ktery byl pouzit a zmackan do kulicky.

Notes: An empty can of popular soft drink Starch Kola.
Displayed Text: Prazdna plechovka oblibeneho nealkoholickeho napoje Starch Kola.

Notes: A discarded packet of deep fried potato batons.
A decorative cup awarded as a prize.
A stuffed fabric pillow.
A roll of thin paper sheets.
A roll of woven fabric used to bind up wounds.
Displayed Text: Role tkane latky, ktera se pouziva k prevazovani ran.

Notes: A Print Scanner.
A pair of lockable metal cuffs which fasten around a prisoner's wrists.
Displayed Text: Par uzamykatelnych kovovych pout, ktera se upevnuji kolem zapesti vezne.

Notes: A yellow, felt-covered ball used in the sport of tennis.
Displayed Text: Zluty micek potazeny plsti, ktery se pouziva v tenisu.

Notes: A square paper napkin that has been used.
Displayed Text: Ctvercovy papirovy ubrousek, ktery byl pouzit.

Notes: Leather wallet containing an old badge for the |city.name| Police.
Displayed Text: Kozena penezenka se starym odznakem policie |city.name|.

Notes: A crumpled sheet of paper.
A device used for breaking numeric codes. Can be used on keypads or even keyboards.
Displayed Text: Zarizeni pouzivane k lamani ciselnych kodu. Lze pouzit na klavesnici nebo i na klavesnici.

Notes: When within range, possible interactions will be displayed at the bottom of the screen.
Displayed Text: Pokud je v dosahu, zobrazi se mozne interakce v dolni casti obrazovky.

Notes: You can run by holding |controls.sprint|, crouch using |controls.crouch| and jump with |controls.jump|.
Displayed Text: Behat muzete podrzenim |controls.sprint|, krcit se pomoci |controls.crouch| a skakat pomoci |controls.jump|.

Notes: Many items in the world can be inspected in detail using the 'Inspect' interaction. When you do this, a new folder that contains information about the item is displayed and the game is paused.
Displayed Text: Mnoho polozek ve svete lze podrobne zkontrolovat pomoci interakce 'Inspect'. Pri tomto ukonu se zobrazi nova slozka s informacemi o predmetu a hra se pozastavi.

Notes: When you inspect an item, it brings up its evidence window. This can be pinned to your case board for future reference using the pin at the top.
Displayed Text: Pri kontrole polozky se zobrazi jeji evidencni okno. To si muzete pripnout na nastenku pripadu pro budouci pouziti pomoci spendliku v horni casti.

Notes: The City Directory is a commonly found world item that lists the address of every citizen in the city, indexed via their first initial and surname.
Displayed Text: Adresar mesta je bezne dostupny ve svete, kde je uvedena adresa kazdeho obcana mesta, indexovana podle krestniho jmena a prijmeni.

Notes: You also have access to a city district map that you can toggle in the upper left in the case screen, or view in-game with |controls.map|.
Displayed Text: Mate take pristup k mape mestske ctvrti, kterou muzete prepnout v levem hornim rohu na obrazovce pripadu nebo zobrazit ve hre pomoci |controls.map|.

Notes: To know if a door is locked or not, you'll first have to try and open it. Locked doors can be unlocked by focusing on the door handle. If you have the correct key for the door, you'll see an interaction option to unlock/lock it.
Displayed Text: Chcete-li zjistit, zda jsou dvere zamcene, musite je nejprve zkusit otevrit. Zamcene dvere lze odemknout zamerenim na kliku. Pokud mate pro dane dvere spravny klic, zobrazi se moznost interakce pro jejich odemknuti/zamknuti.

Notes: Passcodes in Shadows of Doubt are always a 4 digit numeric code. If you're lucky, you'll be able to discover them by finding various notes.
Displayed Text: Pristupove kody ve hre Shadows of Doubt jsou vzdy ctyrmistne. Pokud budete mit stesti, podari se vam je odhalit nalezenim ruznych poznamek.

Notes: There may be points during gameplay where you want to advance time at a significant rate. To do this you can either sleep at your apartment, or find somewhere public to sit down to wait.
Displayed Text: Behem hry mohou nastat okamziky, kdy budete chtit vyrazne zrychlit cas. Za timto ucelem muzete bud prespat ve svem byte, nebo si najit nejake verejne misto, kde si muzete sednout a pockat.

Notes: You can return to your apartment at any time in the game to catch a break. To find your apartment, open the map and use the small button with the house icon to the upper left. This will open the folder; you can then plot a route in the same way you would for any other location.
Displayed Text: Kdykoli ve hre se muzete vratit do sveho bytu a odpocinout si. Chcete-li najit svuj byt, otevrete mapu a pouzijte male tlacitko s ikonou domu vlevo nahore. Tim se otevre slozka; pote si muzete naplanovat trasu stejnym zpusobem jako pro jakoukoli jinou lokaci.

Notes: A citizen profile can be build using unique traits: Their full name, their voice, their photo/image/likeness, or their fingerprint.
Displayed Text: Profil obcana lze vytvorit pomoci jedinecnych vlastnosti: Jmeno a prijmeni, hlas, fotografie/obrazek/podoba nebo otisk prstu.

Notes: If all else fails, you can attempt to barge through a door. Sprint at the door by holding |controls.sprint| and when you are close, use |controls.secondary|. It may take several attempts, depending on your strength. It's also very loud!
Displayed Text: Pokud vse ostatni selze, muzete se pokusit proniknout dvermi. Ke dverim sprintujte podrzenim |controls.sprint| a az budete blizko, pouzijte |controls.secondary|. V zavislosti na vasi sile to muze trvat nekolik pokusu. Je to take velmi hlasite!

Notes: You can travel through buildings via ventilation ducts. Simply open the grate, then select the action to climb through. Do the same to get out. Ducts are a great way to sneak around.
Displayed Text: Ventilacnimi kanaly muzete prochazet budovami. Staci otevrit mriz a pak vybrat akci, kterou chcete prolezt. Totez provedte, chcete-li se dostat ven. Potrubi je skvely zpusob, jak se plizit.

Notes: Not being seen is your best chance of survival. The central cursor displays the information you need to stay hidden.
Displayed Text: Neviditelnost je nejlepsi sanci na preziti. Centralni kurzor zobrazuje informace, ktere potrebujete, abyste zustali skryti.

Notes: When things go wrong you may choose to resort to combat. To do this, select your fists using the inventory menu (|controls.weaponselect|).
Displayed Text: Kdyz se neco nepovede, muzete se uchylit k boji. To provedete tak, ze v nabidce inventare (|controls.weaponselect|) vyberete pesti.

Notes: If you're shady you may accrue some felonies. These are displayed in the same way as statuses.
Displayed Text: Pokud jste podezreli, muzete si pripsat nekolik trestnych cinu. Ty se zobrazuji stejne jako statusy.

Notes: Alarms are triggered in two ways: either through alarm panels on walls or by security systems.
Displayed Text: Alarmy se spousteji dvema zpusoby: bud prostrednictvim poplasnych panelu na stenach, nebo bezpecnostnimi systemy.

Notes: Money can be used to buy items in the world, acquire genetic upgrades for your character, pay for information, decorate your apartment, or even buy a new one.
Displayed Text: Penize muzete pouzit na nakup predmetu ve svete, porizeni genetickych vylepseni pro svou postavu, zaplaceni informaci, vyzdobu bytu nebo dokonce koupi noveho.

Notes: Upgrades can be stolen, rewarded or purchased in the form of SyncDisks. These are small cassettes that can be used with rejuvenation sequencers to effectively alter a host's DNA.
Displayed Text: Upgrady lze ukrast, ziskat za odmenu nebo zakoupit ve forme SyncDisku. Jedna se o male kazety, ktere lze pouzit s omlazovacimi sekvenatory k ucinne zmene DNA hostitele.

Notes: You may find telephones throughout your exploration of the world. Each telephone has a telephone number, and you can perform several basic actions including: finding out the telephone number, finding out who last called this telephone or calling an enforcer squad.
Displayed Text: Na telefony muzete narazit pri svem objevovani sveta. Kazdy telefon ma sve telefonni cislo a vy muzete provest nekolik zakladnich akci, mezi ktere patri: zjisteni telefonniho cisla, zjisteni, kdo naposledy na tento telefon volal, nebo zavolani jednotky vymahacu.

Notes: Crunchers are digital personal computation devices. They're common in most apartments and white-collar workplaces. If you know a citizen's passcode, you can log into their account. From here you may be able to find a wealth of information.
Displayed Text: Crunchery jsou digitalni osobni vypocetni zarizeni. Jsou bezne ve vetsine bytu a na pracovistich bilych limecku. Pokud znate pristupovy kod obcana, muzete se prihlasit k jeho uctu. Odtud se vam muze podarit zjistit mnozstvi informaci.

Notes: Each citizen in the city has a unique fingerprint. You can scan for them using the fingerprint scanner device in your inventory (access with |controls.weaponselect|).
Displayed Text: Kazdy obcan mesta ma jedinecny otisk prstu. Muzete je naskenovat pomoci zarizeni pro snimani otisku prstu v inventari (pristup pomoci |controls.weaponselect|).

Notes: Footprints are not unique to each citizen, but may be useful evidence nevertheless. Prints come in a range of sizes and will  be either from a regular shoe, a boot or a heel.
Displayed Text: Stopy nejsou pro kazdeho obcana jedinecne, ale presto mohou byt uzitecnym dukazem. Otisky jsou ruznych velikosti a pochazeji bud z bezne boty, nebo z boty na podpatku.

Notes: Blood spatter can often communicate how a citizen was killed.
Displayed Text: Krevni skvrny mohou casto informovat o tom, jak byl obcan zabit.

Notes: One of the things you'll want to try and determine at a murder scene is how the victim was killed. Often there are enough clues to determine the category of the weapon.
Displayed Text: Jednou z veci, ktere se na miste vrazdy snazite zjistit, je zpusob, jakym byla obet zabita. Casto existuje dostatek voditek k urceni kategorie zbrane.

Notes: Citizens can sometimes provide answers. Some may want money in exchange for information, some may not want to talk at all.
Displayed Text: Obcane mohou nekdy poskytnout odpovedi. Nekteri mohou chtit vymenou za informace penize, jini nemusi chtit mluvit vubec.

Notes: To access your inventory use |controls.weaponselect|. This opens a menu displaying your current inventory and status.
Displayed Text: Pro pristup do inventare pouzijte |controls.weaponselect|. Otevre se nabidka zobrazujici vas aktualni inventar a stav.

Notes: Depending on your activity, different kinds of status may affect your character: these are displayed on the left of the screen.
Displayed Text: V zavislosti na vasi cinnosti mohou vasi postavu ovlivnit ruzne druhy stavu: ty jsou zobrazeny v leve casti obrazovky.

Notes: Enforcers are corporate sponsored security personnel who will respond to law infringements. There are usually several on duty at any one time, though like every other citizen, they have lives outside of work.
Displayed Text: Strazci zakona jsou bezpecnostni pracovnici sponzorovani spolecnosti, kteri reaguji na poruseni zakona. Ve sluzbe jich obvykle byva nekolik, i kdyz stejne jako kazdy jiny obcan maji i oni sve mimopracovni zivoty.

Notes: The sound icons next to the possible actions show how loud performing these actions will be. Each icon roughly represents roughly 5 meters of audibility, although closed doors and walls will affect this.
Displayed Text: Ikony zvuku vedle moznych akci ukazuji, jak hlasite bude jejich provedeni. Kazda ikona predstavuje zhruba 5 metru slysitelnosti, ackoli zavrene dvere a steny tuto hodnotu ovlivnuji.

Notes: Too dark? You also have a flashlight you can toggle with |controls.flashlight|.
Displayed Text: Prilis tmave? K dispozici mate take svitilnu, kterou muzete prepinat pomoci |controls.flashlight|.

Notes:
Often this folder will feature multiple tabs that you can switch between. These tabs are context sensitive, but the most common tabs are:

Summary: displays immediate information such as a summary, image or the contents of a document.

Facts: collated facts that have been discovered relating to this evidence. Useful for following links between various pieces of evidence
Displayed Text:
Tato slozka casto obsahuje vice karet, mezi kterymi muzete prepinat. Tyto karty jsou kontextove zavisle, ale nejcasteji se pouzivaji tyto karty:

Souhrn: zobrazuje okamzite informace, jako je shrnuti, obrazek nebo obsah dokumentu.

Fakty: shrnuti faktu, ktere byly zjisteny v souvislosti s timto dukazem. Uzitecne pro sledovani souvislosti mezi ruznymi dukazy.

Notes: With most items, you can also pin the reference to your case board. This effectively bookmarks the evidence, so you can quickly come back to it when needed.
Displayed Text: U vetsiny polozek muzete take pripnout odkaz na nastenku kufriku. Tim si dukazni material efektivne ulozite do zalozek, takze se k nemu muzete v pripade potreby rychle vratit.

Notes: Pinned items are displayed as icons that you can move around on the board by dragging their pin. You can position these items you wish, and select them to bring up their evidence window.
Displayed Text: Pripnute polozky se zobrazuji jako ikony, ktere muzete na tabuli presouvat pretazenim jejich kolicku. Tyto polozky muzete libovolne umistit a jejich vyberem vyvolat jejich evidencni okno.

Notes: Facts or connections are displayed as string, you can mouse over these to see more info.
Displayed Text: Fakta nebo spojeni se zobrazuji jako retezec, na ktery muzete mysi najet a zobrazit dalsi informace.

Notes: Due to the sheer amount of information, you can't pin it to your case board. To look up an address, you'll have to find a physical copy in the game world.
Displayed Text: Vzhledem k velkemu mnozstvi informaci ji nemuzete pripnout na nastenku. Chcete-li vyhledat adresu, musite najit jeji fyzickou kopii ve svete hry.

Notes: Public companies do not need to be looked up with the Directory as they are labelled on your map (although they are also listed).
Displayed Text: Verejne spolecnosti neni treba vyhledavat v adresari, protoze jsou oznaceny na mape (i kdyz jsou take uvedeny).

Notes: Clicking on an entry will bring up an address that can be inspected as an evidence item and pinned to your case board, just like other world objects.\n
Displayed Text: Kliknutim na polozku se zobrazi adresa, kterou lze zkontrolovat jako dukazni predmet a pripnout na nastenku pripadu, stejne jako ostatni objekty sveta.\n

Notes: With addresses and locations, you can use the 'plot route' button on the summary tab to toggle a route-finding arrow which will guide you towards the destination.
Displayed Text: U adres a mist muzete pomoci tlacitka 'vykreslit trasu' na karte Souhrn prepnout sipku pro vyhledavani trasy, ktera vas navede k cili.

Notes: You can use the map to inspect locations and addresses and plot routes.
Displayed Text: Pomoci mapy muzete kontrolovat mista a adresy a zakreslovat trasy.

Notes: Many locations must be discovered first-hand (you have to visit them) in order for them to appear on your map.
Displayed Text: Mnoha mista musite objevit z prvni ruky (musite je navstivit), aby se objevila na vasi mape.

Notes: If you don't have a key you'll also have the option of lock-picking it. This will take time and is an 'illegal action' meaning citizens will confront you if you are seen.
Displayed Text: Pokud klic nemate, muzete ho take vylomit (pomoci lock-picku). To zabere nejaky cas a jedna se o 'nezakonnou akci', coz znamena, ze vas obcane budou konfrontovat, pokud vas uvidi.

Notes: You can also opt to knock on a door if you are trying to talk to somebody inside (or simply trying to attract their attention). If anybody is home they will likely open the door to greet you.
Displayed Text: Muzete take zaklepat na dvere, pokud se snazite s nekym uvnitr promluvit (nebo jen upoutat jeho pozornost). Pokud je nekdo doma, pravdepodobne vam otevre a pozdravi vas.

Notes: Some doors can feature key-code locks. You'll have to discover the correct code to unlock them, or use a 'Codebreaker' device.
Displayed Text: Nektere dvere mohou byt vybaveny zamky s kodem na klic. K jejich odemceni musite zjistit spravny kod nebo pouzit zarizeni'Codebreaker'.

Notes: Your apartment is also displayed on your map with a house icon.
Displayed Text: Vas byt se take zobrazi na mape s ikonou domu.

Notes: As each of the above is unique to them, you can link this information together, resulting in a more complete profile. Certain sources will be more useful than others for this: for example, a citizen's workplace ID may allow you to tie their name to photo.
Displayed Text: Vzhledem k tomu, ze kazdy z vyse uvedenych udaju je pro ne jedinecny, muzete tyto informace propojit, cimz ziskate uplnejsi profil. Nektere zdroje budou pro tento ucel uzitecnejsi nez jine: napriklad prukaz obcana na pracovisti vam muze umoznit spojit jeho jmeno s fotografii.

Notes: Each lock has it's own strength. When you start the process by interacting with the door handle or lock, the indicated bars will tell you how many picks you need to complete the lock-pick.
Displayed Text: Kazdy zamek ma svou vlastni silu. Kdyz zahajite proces interakci s klikou dveri nebo zamkem, indikovane sloupce vam reknou, kolik lock-picku potrebujete k dokonceni prolomeni zamku.

Notes: You can also use lock-picks to sabotage security systems.
Displayed Text: K sabotazi bezpecnostnich systemu muzete pouzit take lock-picky.

Notes: Any ducts you travel down will also be added to your map.
Displayed Text: Do mapy se pridaji take vsechny kanaly, kterymi projdete.

Notes: The dot in the very middle of the screen displays how hidden you are: a hollow circle means you are completely obscured and others will only notice you if you get extremely close. A filled in circle means you are completely visible.
Displayed Text: Tecka uprostred obrazovky ukazuje, jak moc jste skryti: prazdny kruh znamena, ze jste zcela zakryti a ostatni si vas vsimnou, jen pokud se dostanete velmi blizko. Vyplneny kruh znamena, ze jste zcela viditelni.

Notes: The color of the outer eye shape displays if someone or something can see you: if it turns red a citizen or security system has spotted you, so it's time to run!
Displayed Text: Barva vnejsiho tvaru oka ukazuje, zda vas nekdo nebo neco vidi: pokud se zmeni na cervenou, spatril vas obcan nebo bezpecnostni system, takze je cas utect!

Notes: You can choose to punch or block. If you block at the right time you'll automatically perform a counter move that knocks out the other citizen.
Displayed Text: Muzete si vybrat, zda chcete uderit, nebo blokovat. Pokud zablokujete ve spravny okamzik, automaticky provedete protipohyb, ktery vyradi druheho obcana.

Notes: But be careful detective, violence can escalate quickly!
Displayed Text: Ale pozor, detektive, nasili se muze rychle stupnovat!

Notes: Alarm panels can be manually triggered by a citizen if they see wrong-doing.
Displayed Text: Poplachove panely muze obcan spustit rucne, pokud vidi, ze se deje neco nekaleho.

Notes: Security cameras will attempt to focus on you if they detect wrong-doing, such as trespassing or any other illegal action. You'll have a brief warning period to avoid their targeting, after which the alarm will be sounded.
Displayed Text: Bezpecnostni kamery se na vas pokusi zamerit, pokud zjisti protipravni jednani, napriklad vniknuti na cizi pozemek nebo jine nezakonne jednani. Budete mit kratkou dobu na to, abyste se vyhnuli jejich zamereni, pote se spusti alarm.

Notes: If the alarm is triggered it will sound throughout the entire building. And if the alarm was sounded on you, you'll have a period of time where you are 'wanted' in that building, and security systems will automatically target you.
Displayed Text: Pokud se alarm spusti, rozezni se v cele budove. A pokud byl poplach spusten na vas, bude po urcitou dobu po vas v budove 'vyhlaseno patrani' a bezpecnostni systemy se na vas automaticky zameri.

Notes: Furthermore, large security doors will be deployed on the floor the alarm was triggered on, in an attempt to seal off the exit.
Displayed Text: Krome toho budou v patre, kde byl spusten alarm, rozmisteny velke bezpecnostni dvere, ktere se pokusi uzavrit vychod.

Notes: Building alarms will eventually reset.
Displayed Text: Alarmy v budovach se nakonec resetuji.

Notes: You can use this information to further your investigation. In addition to this you might also find a large metal cabinet in the lobby or basement of some buildings: this is the telephone router. It records incoming and outgoing calls.
Displayed Text: Tyto informace muzete pouzit k dalsimu vysetrovani. Krome toho muzete v hale nebo suterenu nekterych budov najit velkou kovovou skrin: jedna se o telefonni smerovac. Zaznamenava prichozi a odchozi hovory.

Notes: In regards to outgoing calls, the router will only tell you which building the call was routed to. But in regards to incoming calls, it will also display which address within the building the call is being routed to. This means you can effectively trace a call by first accessing the router in the building the call was being made from, then doing the same for the building the call was routed to.
Displayed Text: Pokud jde o odchozi hovory, smerovac vam sdeli pouze to, do ktere budovy byl hovor smerovan. V pripade prichozich hovoru vsak zobrazi take adresu v budove, na kterou je hovor smerovan. To znamena, ze muzete ucinne sledovat hovor tak, ze nejprve vstoupite do smerovace v budove, ze ktere byl hovor uskutecnen, a pote provedete totez pro budovu, do ktere byl hovor smerovan.

Notes: Once logged on, you'll be able to access V-mails, which are personal or work-related messages sent between citizens.
Displayed Text: Po prihlaseni budete mit pristup k V-mailum, coz jsou osobni nebo pracovni zpravy zasilane mezi obcany.

Notes: Unknown fingerprints will be found in 'sets', with 'set A' being the first you find. Any matching prints will also be labeled to that corresponding set.
Displayed Text: Nezname otisky prstu budou nalezeny v 'sadach', pricemz 'sada A' je prvni nalezena sada. Vsechny shodne otisky budou rovnez oznaceny k prislusne sade.

Notes: For example, if you find 'set A' at an apartment and subsequently at a bar, you can prove a citizen was in both locations at some point.
Displayed Text: Pokud napriklad najdete 'sadu A' v byte a nasledne v baru, muzete prokazat, ze se obcan v urcitem okamziku nachazel na obou mistech.

Notes: Use |controls.secondary| to inspect fingerprints after you've found them to pin them to your case board. Fingerprints may disappear over time.
Displayed Text: Po nalezeni otisku prstu je pomoci |controls.secondary| zkontrolujte a pripnete je na desku kufriku. Otisky prstu mohou casem zmizet.

Notes: You can call enforcers using a telephone.
Surveillance footage will capture a citizen's likeness, and if they also work at that location; their name.
Displayed Text: Zaznamy z bezpecnostnich kamer zachycuji podobu obcana, a pokud na danem miste pracuje, take jeho jmeno.

Notes: Crunchers only store surveillance information for about 24 hours.
Displayed Text: Crunchery uchovavaji informace o sledovani pouze po dobu priblizne 24 hodin.

Notes: You can print stills from CCTV surveillance to use as evidence.
Displayed Text: Muzete vytisknout snimky z kameroveho systemu a pouzit je jako dukazni material.

Notes: |type| located at the |building| building on |street|.
A street in |city.name|.
A building located on |street|.
I don't know what |name| looks like...
I don't know who this is...
A camera that can be used to take photographs.
An electronic device that can be placed on keypads or keyboards to brute-force access codes. Single use.
Displayed Text: Elektronicke zarizeni, ktere lze umistit na klavesnice nebo klavesnice a vynutit si tak pristupove kody. Jednorazove pouziti.

Notes: A coin that can be used to create distraction.\n\nOfficially a 'credit', but colloquially known as a 'crow' thanks to the image of a bird on the side.

Notes:
Dearest |receiver.firstname|,

I can't start at the beginning, so I'll start at the end: forgive me. I'm sorry to do this to you – there's no other way. This place has taken anything good that was left in me. 

Anything of value I have, it's yours. There's a Will at the office. Please – use the crows to get away from here, out from underneath it all. Somewhere else, where you might have a chance. 

|writer.name|
Displayed Text:
Nejdrazsi |receiver.firstname|,

Nemohu zacit od zacatku, takze zacnu od konce: odpustte mi. Omlouvam se, ze jsem ti to udelal - neni jina moznost. Tohle misto mi vzalo vsechno dobre, co ve mne zustalo. 

Vsechno, co mam, je tvoje. V kancelari je Will. Prosim - pouzij vrany, aby ses odsud dostal pryc, pryc od toho vseho. Nekam jinam, kde bys mohl mit sanci. 

|writer.name|

We must see higher sea levels as an opportunity,' states Tanner Indigo, of Kensington Indigo. 'Thanks to our investment in hover technologies, over water travel has become a boom industry!'

Since the decline of the automobile, the global transportation industry has contracted by almost 70%. There are hopes to reverse the decline by investing in alternate transport technology.

Pan Indigo se odmitl vyjadrit k umrti sveho byvaleho partnera Eugena Kensingtona pri nehode vznasedla pred nekolika lety.

Notes: A valuable gem
A chemical spray, used for cleaning surfaces
Displayed Text: Chemicky sprej, ktery se pouziva k cisteni povrchu

Notes: A glass jar for storing Starch-brand snacks
Displayed Text: Sklenena nadoba na uchovavani obcerstveni znacky Starch

Notes: A metal can containing oil
A set containing instruments for simple chemistry experiments

Notes: Japanese dumplings made with rice flour
Twisted fried dough, sprinkled with Starch sugar

Notes: A cream-filled pastry, popular in the Old Empire
Displayed Text: Pecivo se smetanovou naplni, oblibene ve Stare risi.

Notes: Escape to the streets to eliminate your wanted fines, but be careful not to spend too long in the cold.
Displayed Text: Utecte do ulic, abyste odstranili hledane pokuty, ale dejte si pozor, abyste v mrazu nestravili prilis dlouhou dobu.

Notes: Smashing objects, throwing things, breaking windows and littering are all classed as vandalism under corporate law.
Displayed Text: Rozbijeni predmetu, hazeni veci, rozbijeni oken a znecistovani odpadky jsou podle firemniho prava povazovany za vandalismus.

Notes: Follow the cables from security systems to discover a breaker box: use this to override connected devices for a short amount of time.
Displayed Text: Po kabelech od bezpecnostnich systemu objevite jisticovou skrin: pomoci ni muzete na kratkou dobu vyradit pripojena zarizeni.

Notes: Illegal businesses can be found in secret back rooms and basements.
Displayed Text: Nelegalni podniky se nachazeji v tajnych zadnich mistnostech a sklepich.

Notes: Yeah, I got a job. Need someone taken care of.
Displayed Text: Jo, mam praci. Potrebuju se o nekoho postarat.

Notes: Deliver it under the door at |sidejob.poster.home.name|.
Keep a lookout for paper-clips and hair pins: these can be used for picking locks.
Displayed Text: Davejte pozor na kancelarske sponky a sponky do vlasu: lze je pouzit k odemykani zamku.

Notes: Peek under doors by looking near the bottom edge and selecting 'Peek'.
Displayed Text: Podivejte se pod dvere tak, ze se podivate na spodni okraj a vyberete moznost 'Peek'.

Notes: You can use |controls.caseboard| to pause at any time and examine your case board.
Displayed Text: Pomoci |controls.caseboard| muzete kdykoli pozastavit praci a prohlednout si desku kufriku.

Notes: Computers are referred to as 'number crunchers', 'micro crunchers' or simply 'crunchers'.
Displayed Text: Pocitace se oznacuji jako 'pocitaci stroje', 'mikropocitaci stroje' nebo proste 'pocitaci stroje'.

Notes: Citizens are lazy. They use the same passcodes for everything, including keypads and cruncher (computer) logins.
Displayed Text: Obcane jsou lini. Pouzivaji stejne pristupove kody pro vsechno, vcetne klavesnic a prihlasovacich udaju k pocitacum.

Notes: Computers are referred to as 'number crunchers', 'micro crunchers' or simply 'crunchers'.
Displayed Text: Pocitace se oznacuji jako 'pocitaci stroje', 'mikropocitaci stroje' nebo proste 'pocitaci stroje'.

Notes: If you find useful evidence on a Micro Cruncher, don't forget to print it using the onscreen print button so you can pin it to your case board.
Displayed Text: Pokud v nastroji Micro Cruncher najdete uzitecne dukazy, nezapomente si je vytisknout pomoci tlacitka tisku na obrazovce, abyste si je mohli pripnout na nastenku pripadu.

Notes: You can adjust the game difficulty at any time using the gameplay options in the main menu.
Displayed Text: Obtiznost hry muzete kdykoli upravit pomoci hernich moznosti v hlavni nabidce.

Notes: Starch Kola are the world's oldest megacorporation, known for producing kola products and snack foods.
Displayed Text: Spolecnost Starch Kola je nejstarsi megakorporaci na svete, ktera je znama vyrobou kolovych vyrobku a pochutin.

Notes: Starch Kola was founded in 1900 during the Mustard War, when their kola was distributed to soldiers as a cure for radiation sickness.
Displayed Text: Spolecnost Starch Kola byla zalozena v roce 1900 behem horcicne valky, kdy byla jeji kola distribuovana vojakum jako lek proti nemoci z ozareni.

Notes: In 1965 Starch Kola was elected President of the United Atlantic States, becoming the first corporation in the world to govern a nation.
Displayed Text: V roce 1965 byl Starch Kola zvolen prezidentem Spojenych statu atlantskych a stal se tak prvni korporaci na svete, ktera vladla statu.

Notes: Apple Krueger is the daughter of late businessman Eden Krueger and is the current acting president of Starch Kola.
Displayed Text: Apple Kruegerova je dcerou zesnuleho podnikatele Edena Kruegera a v soucasnosti je uradujici prezidentkou spolecnosti Starch Kola.

Notes: A Krueger Sandwich consists of synthetic beef, pork and chicken topped with ketchup. It was invented by Eden Krueger to demonstrate the safety of synthetic meat after the Eastern Food Crisis.
Displayed Text: Kruegeruv sendvic se sklada ze syntetickeho hoveziho, veproveho a kureciho masa, ktere je prelite kecupem. Vymyslel ho Eden Krueger, aby demonstroval bezpecnost syntetickeho masa po vychodni potravinove krizi.

Notes: A 'Kapple Pie' is a sweet apple pie drenched in kola syrup. It was invented by Starch Kola to celebrate Apple Kreuger's induction to the board of the company.
Displayed Text: 'Kapple Pie' je sladky jablecny kolac zality kolovym sirupem. Vymyslela ho spolecnost Starch Kola na oslavu uvedeni Apple Kreugera do predstavenstva spolecnosti.

Notes: The Red Gums are a pseudo-religious group who worship capitalism and social mobility. They equate the Echelons of the city, home to the social elite, with heaven, and the slums with hell.
Displayed Text: Rude gumy jsou pseudonabozenska skupina, ktera uctiva kapitalismus a socialni mobilitu. Eselony mesta, kde zije spolecenska elita, prirovnavaji k nebi a chudinske ctvrti k peklu.

Notes: The fanatical Red Gums associate themselves with Starch Kola. Rumour has it they perform blood sacrifices to the late Eden Krueger, despite the fact he never acknowledged them during his lifetime.
Displayed Text: Fanaticti Red Gums se spojuji se skrobovou kolou. Proslycha se, ze provadeji krvave obeti zesnulemu Edenu Kruegerovi, prestoze je za sveho zivota nikdy neuznal.

Notes: LEM are a revolutionary group opposed to rule by capitalism and dedicated to bringing in a new form of socialist government. Their name is a reference to the term 'levée en masse', associated with a huge uprising of everyday people.
Displayed Text: LEM je revolucni skupina, ktera se stavi proti vlade kapitalismu a usiluje o zavedeni nove formy socialisticke vlady. Jejich nazev je odkazem na termin 'levee en masse', spojeny s obrovskym povstanim obycejnych lidi.

Notes: Although the LEM movement is gathering popularity, many citizens see it as a lost cause, and will refer to its members as 'lemmings'.
Displayed Text: Ackoli hnuti LEM ziskava na popularite, mnozi obcane ho povazuji za ztraceny pripad a jeho cleny oznacuji za 'lemply'.

Notes: Founded by Eugene Kensington and Tanner Indigo, Kensington Indigo began as an investment bank. Eventually the company took on a more aggressive role within the corporate world, investing resources into taking down their competitors.
Displayed Text: Spolecnost Kensington Indigo, kterou zalozili Eugene Kensington a Tanner Indigo, zacinala jako investicni banka. Nakonec spolecnost prevzala agresivnejsi roli ve firemnim svete a investovala prostredky do likvidace svych konkurentu.

Notes: Founded by Kyra Cho, Kaizen-6 is a giant technology company that has risen to prominence thanks to their dating service, 'Dove'. Users are able to send and receive dating profiles via V-Mail.
Displayed Text: Kaizen-6 je obri technologicka spolecnost, kterou zalozila Kyra Cho a ktera se proslavila diky sve seznamovaci sluzbe 'Dove'. Uzivatele mohou posilat a prijimat seznamovaci profily prostrednictvim V-Mailu.

Notes: Kaizen-6 have recently negotiated deals with to allow inter-corporation dating via their 'Dove' service. Inter-corp dating is usually strongly discouraged.
Displayed Text: Spolecnost Kaizen-6 nedavno uzavrela dohody, ktere umoznuji seznamovani mezi korporacemi prostrednictvim sluzby 'Dove'. Seznamovani mezi spolecnostmi se obvykle durazne nedoporucuje.

Notes: Headed by the mysterious Evangeline Elliott, Elliott Genetics, commonly known as El-Gen, rose to fame thanks to their cosmetic Sequence Rejuvenation programme.
Displayed Text: Spolecnost Elliott Genetics, znama jako El-Gen, vedena tajemnou Evangeline Elliott, se proslavila diky svemu kosmetickemu programu Sekvencni omlazeni.

Notes: Candor are a global news group founded by married couple Alvin Estrada and Grover Dalton, famous for their turbulent relationship.
Displayed Text: Candor je celosvetova zpravodajska skupina, kterou zalozil manzelsky par Alvin Estrada a Grover Dalton, znamy svym bourlivym vztahem.

Notes: Credits are more commonly known by their slang name 'crows'
Displayed Text: Kredity jsou zname spise pod slangovym nazvem 'crows'.
Alternate Text: diky obrazkum starych anglickych ptaku na mincich.

Notes: The Myriads is the nickname given to the largest, most densely populated area of a city where ordinary 'Class 2' citizens live. The Myriads begin at ground level and rise through low to middling floors.
Displayed Text: Myriady je prezdivka pro nejvetsi a nejhusteji osidlenou oblast mesta, kde ziji bezni obcane tridy 2. Myriady zacinaji na urovni prizemi a stoupaji pres nizka az do strednich pater.

Notes: The Echelons are where the wealthy elite reside, on upper floors high above the pollution.
Displayed Text: V hornich patrech vysoko nad znecistenim sidli bohata elita.

Notes: Subterranean levels of the city are known as The Fathoms, prone to flooding and home to outcasts, criminals and 'undesirable' citizens.
Displayed Text: Podzemni urovne mesta jsou zname jako Sahove, jsou nachylne k zaplavam a jsou domovem vydedencu, zlocincu a 'nezadoucich' obcanu.

Notes: The Fields is a suburban retirement district outside the city. Eligibility requirements are strict and substantial life savings are needed.
Displayed Text: Fields je predmestska duchodcovska ctvrt za mestem. Pozadavky na zpusobilost jsou prisne a je treba mit znacne zivotni uspory.

Notes: V-Mail (short for Vacuum Mail) is a large, city-wide network of pneumatic pipes used to deliver messages to crunchers via the use of compressed air.
Displayed Text: V-Mail (zkratka pro Vacuum Mail) je rozsahla sit pneumatickych potrubi, ktera se pouziva k dorucovani zprav do schranky pomoci stlaceneho vzduchu.

Notes: The United Atlantic States (UAS) are a loose collective of countries from western Europe and North America, governed by a single corporation.
Displayed Text: Spojene staty atlanticke (SA) jsou volnym spolecenstvim zemi zapadni Evropy a Severni Ameriky, ktere ridi jedna korporace.

Notes: 'The Old Empire' is the name given to the Anglo-French Empire, which ruled most of the western world until the Mustard War of 1891.
Displayed Text: 'Stare imperium' je oznaceni pro anglo-francouzske imperium, ktere vladlo vetsine zapadniho sveta az do horcicne valky v roce 1891.

Notes: Got that? Take a photo, or it didn't happen.
Displayed Text: Rozumite? Vyfotte to, jinak se to nestalo.

Notes: Need more money? Try looking for jobs on notice boards near public telephones in bars or social spaces.
Displayed Text: Potrebujete vice penez? Zkuste hledat praci na nastenkach u verejnych telefonu v barech nebo ve spolecenskych prostorach.

Notes: Crunchers (computers) in back offices or security rooms often give access to the CCTV cameras and security systems.
Displayed Text: Pristup ke kameram CCTV a bezpecnostnim systemum casto umoznuji pocitace v zazemi kancelari nebo v bezpecnostnich mistnostech.

Building telephone routers can often be found in basements or on the ground floor in a utility room. Use them to access telephone call data from the building.
Displayed Text: Telefonni smerovace v budovach se casto nachazeji ve sklepe nebo v prizemi v technicke mistnosti. Pomoci nich ziskate pristup k udajum o telefonnich hovorech z budovy.

Notes: They work at |receiver.job.employer.name|.
Telephone routers inside buildings will tell you the exact origin or destination of a call if either took place in that building. Otherwise they will detail only the other building.
Displayed Text: Telefonni smerovace uvnitr budov vam sdeli presny puvod nebo cil hovoru, pokud k nemu doslo v dane budove. V opacnem pripade uvedou pouze podrobnosti o druhe budove.

Notes: Security can be disabled from the relevant cruncher: look for the back room office of a company, or a separate security control room for a whole building.
Displayed Text: Zabezpeceni muze byt vypnuto z prislusneho chrlice: hledejte zazemi kancelare spolecnosti nebo samostatny bezpecnostni dispecink pro celou budovu.

Notes: Sneaking up to a citizen from behind will present you with the option to search them. You will often find a form of ID.
Displayed Text: Kdyz se k obcanovi priplizite zezadu, muzete ho prohledat. Casto u nej najdete prukaz totoznosti.

Notes: You can purchase detective tools from special vending machines at city hall. You may also find some useful items in pawn shops and illegal businesses.

Displayed Text: K prolomeni pristupovych kodu lze pouzit jednorazove zarizeni zvane 'koder'. Muzete si ho zakoupit v automatu na radnici.

Notes: Make sure you're waiting in the warm!
Displayed Text: Ujistete se, ze cekate v teple!

Notes: While inside your apartment, you can edit the decor. Open the inventory menu with |controls.weaponselect| and select the option to edit decor.
Displayed Text: Uvnitr bytu muzete upravovat vyzdobu. Otevrete nabidku inventare pomoci |controls.weaponselect| a vyberte moznost upravit vyzdobu.

Notes: Citizens also have many other non-unique traits, but you can only tie this info to a unique trait.
Displayed Text: Obcane maji take mnoho dalsich nejedinecnych rysu, ale tyto informace muzete vztahnout pouze k jedinecnemu rysu.

Notes: Investigate a citizen's apartment or workplace to gain profile information.
Displayed Text: Prozkoumejte byt nebo pracoviste obcana a ziskejte informace o jeho profilu.

Notes: Be careful! Lock-picking is illegal. If seen, it will often trigger a reaction.
Displayed Text: Budte opatrni! Vylamovani zamku je nezakonne. Pokud je spatreno, casto vyvola reakci.

Notes: You swore off the use of firearms long ago, so guns can only be used by yourself as a melee weapon.
Displayed Text: Na pouzivani strelnych zbrani jste se jiz davno zaprisahli, takze zbrane muzete pouzivat pouze jako zbran pro boj zblizka.

Notes: Listen out for murders being reported by enforcer scanner (automatically triggered) or in the news.
Displayed Text: Davejte pozor na vrazdy, ktere jsou hlaseny skenerem vymahacu (automaticky spustenym) nebo ve zpravach.

Notes: Newspapers may reveal extra clues about the latest murder case.
Displayed Text: Noviny mohou odhalit dalsi stopy k nejnovejsimu pripadu vrazdy.

Notes: You'll be rewarded handsomely by catching a killer, so you may want to prioritise these cases. Start by visiting the crime scene if you can, and gathering as many clues as possbile.
Displayed Text: Za dopadeni vraha budete bohate odmeneni, takze tyto pripady muzete uprednostnit. Zacnete navstevou mista cinu, pokud muzete, a shromazdete co nejvice stop.

Notes: The best thing to do first is build a list of possible suspects; then eliminate them one-by-one. Investigating the victim may also prove useful.
Displayed Text: Nejlepsi je nejprve sestavit seznam moznych podezrelych a pak je jednoho po druhem vyradit. Uzitecne muze byt take vysetrovani obeti.

Notes: If you're caught while these are active, you'll have to pay the fine. Otherwise you can follow the objectives to remove them without penalty.
Displayed Text: Pokud budete pristizeni v dobe, kdy jsou aktivni, budete muset zaplatit pokutu. V opacnem pripade se muzete ridit cili, ktere je odstrani bez pokuty.

Notes: In addition to these systems, be on the look out for laser systems that will activate the alarm if tripped, and poison gas systems that will release toxic gas if the alarm is raised.
Displayed Text: Krome techto systemu si dejte pozor na laserove systemy, ktere v pripade spusteni alarmu aktivuji alarm, a na systemy jedovatych plynu, ktere v pripade spusteni alarmu vypusti jedovaty plyn.

Notes: Loan sharks exist as an illegal business, and will be happy to lend you money as long as you pay them interest on time.
Displayed Text: Lichvari existuji jako nelegalni podnikani a radi vam pujci penize, pokud jim vcas zaplatite uroky.

Notes: With most sync disks, you'll choose between two or three different configuration options. These will be explained in depth in the sync disk interface before install.
Displayed Text: U vetsiny Sync disku si muzete vybrat ze dvou nebo tri ruznych moznosti konfigurace. Ty budou podrobne vysvetleny v rozhrani Sync disku pred instalaci.

Notes: When you have picked up a sync disk, take it to a Sync Clinic to have it installed. Simply use the chamber or a bed, and you should gain the option to install it (or upgrade or uninstall it).
Displayed Text: Po vyzvednuti Sync disku jej odneste na Kliniku Sync, kde vam jej nainstaluji. Staci pouzit komoru nebo luzko a meli byste ziskat moznost instalace (nebo aktualizace ci odinstalace).

Notes: You can also upgrade installed sync disks with upgrade vials. These look like glowing blue syringes, and are extremely vauable. Also take these to a Sync Clinic to use them.
Displayed Text: Nainstalovane Sync disky muzete take aktualizovat pomoci aktualizacnich lahvicek. Ty vypadaji jako svitici modre injekcni strikacky a jsou velmi variabilni. Take je muzete vzit na Kliniku Sync a pouzit je.

Notes: Your print scanner can also detect footprints! Simply aim the scanner at the floor or suspected print and it will do the rest.
Displayed Text: Skener otisku dokaze rozpoznat i otisky nohou! Jednoduse namirte skener na podlahu nebo podezrely otisk a on se postara o zbytek.

Notes: A small amount of forward spatter, along with a larger amount of back spatter may indicate they were shot.
Displayed Text: Male mnozstvi strikancu vpredu a vetsi mnozstvi strikancu vzadu muze naznacovat, ze byly zastreleny.

Notes: A large, thin amount of spatter may be from a laceration from a blade.
Displayed Text: Velke, tenke mnozstvi strikancu muze pochazet z poraneni od cepele.

Notes: A much smaller amount of blood may be evidence of blunt force trauma.
Displayed Text: Mnohem mensi mnozstvi krve muze byt dukazem urazu tupym predmetem.

Notes: Blood mixed with lighter fluids may be evidence that they were poisioned.
Displayed Text: Krev smichana s lehcimi tekutinami muze byt dukazem, ze byly otraveny.

Notes: Wounds: The type of wound on the victim will give you an important clue as to the means of their death.
Displayed Text: Zraneni: Typ zraneni obeti vam poskytne dulezitou informaci o zpusobu jeji smrti.

Notes: Spatter: The blood patterns at the scene can also give you this information.
Displayed Text: Rozstrik: Tuto informaci vam mohou poskytnout i krevni vzorky na miste cinu.

Notes: Expended bullet cartridges: Sometimes the killer may leave these behind at the scene. Be on the lookout for them as they can help identify the weapon used. The cartridges correspond to the following firearms:
Displayed Text: Vypalene nabojnice: Nekdy je vrah muze zanechat na miste cinu. Davejte si na ne pozor, protoze mohou pomoci identifikovat pouzitou zbran. Naboje odpovidaji nasledujicim strelnym zbranim:

Notes: 8mm rounds: Low calibre. Fired from a semi automatic pistol.
Displayed Text: Naboje raze 8 mm: Mala raze. Strili se z poloautomaticke pistole.

Notes: 9x32 rounds: Low calibre. Fired from a revolver.
Displayed Text: 9x32 naboju: Mala raze. Strili se z revolveru.

Notes: .309 rounds: High calibre. Fired from a rifle.
Displayed Text: .309 naboju: Velka raze. Strili se z pusky.

Notes: 12 Gauge Buckshot: Fired from a shotgun.
Deerslug: High calibre. Fired from a shotgun.
Displayed Text: Deerslug: Vysoky kalibr. Strili se z brokovnice.

Notes: Usually a citizen can be bribed to give information.
Displayed Text: Obvykle lze obcana podplatit, aby poskytl informace.

Notes: You can also ask citizens if they have seen anything unusual, which they are more likely to answer versus providing personal information.
Displayed Text: Obcanu se take muzete zeptat, zda nevideli neco neobvykleho, coz je pravdepodobnejsi, nez kdyby poskytli sve osobni udaje.

Notes: Often the type of job will correspond in legality to where you found the posting.
Displayed Text: Typ prace casto odpovida legalnosti mista, kde jste ji nasli.

Notes: You can also find new apartments for sale on these notice boards.
Displayed Text: Na techto nastenkach najdete take nove byty na prodej.

Notes: You can drop or scan picked-up items for fingerprints once an item is selected.
Displayed Text: Po vyberu polozky muzete vyzvednute polozky upustit nebo naskenovat otisky prstu.

Notes: Enforcers aren't interested in solving cases, detective work is outsourced to folks like yourself.
Displayed Text: Vymahaci nemaji zajem resit pripady, detektivni prace je sverena lidem, jako jste vy.

Notes: When you have enough credit, a case will open called 'retirement'. You will be prompted to collect a form at city hall, and name a citizen to receive all your current belongings (these cannot be taken to 'The Fields').
Displayed Text: Kdyz mate dostatek kreditu, otevre se pripad nazvany 'odchod do duchodu'. Budete vyzvani, abyste si na radnici vyzvedli formular a jmenovali obcana, ktery prevezme vsechny vase dosavadni veci (ty nelze odvezt na 'Pole').

Notes: Last Things...
Take care of yourself,\n|story.partnerfirstname|
Work hard, save credits and you too might live out your days in\r\n
Displayed Text: Pracujte tvrde, setrete kredity a mozna i vy dozijete sve dny v\r\n

Notes: The Fields
Do you have what it takes to get away for good?*\n\r\n(eligibility dependent on a citizen credit rating of ”elite” or above)
Displayed Text: Mate na to, abyste mohli odejit navzdy?*\n\r\n(zpusobilost je podminena obcanskym ratingem 'elite' nebo vyssim)

Notes: The Fields
Leave the grind behind forever when you enter |city.name|'s one and only clean air residential district
Displayed Text: Zanechte driny navzdy za sebou, kdyz vstoupite do jedine rezidencni ctvrti |city.name| s cistym vzduchem.

Notes: You’ll know you’re in heaven the moment you set foot in
Displayed Text: V okamziku, kdy vstoupite dovnitr, poznate, ze jste v nebi.

Pick up an application form today!
only citizens with a credit score of elite or higher may access an application form

Notes: That's me...
The Candor Book of World History Volume 1
Displayed Text: Kniha Candor o svetovych dejinach, svazek 1

Notes:
The Eastern Food Crisis

In 1976, sea levels rose to the highest levels since records began. Floods swept the globe. The resulting devastation of infrastructure led to a massive global food shortage, with many countries facing famine. Although the UAS extended a meagre olive branch, to the surprise of many it was Starch Kola founder Eden Krueger who provided the greatest aid. Krueger donated a vast sum of his personal wealth to the cause, funding research into synthetic food substitutes. In 1979, Starch Kola's SynthMeat technology was made public, bringing the food crisis to an end. 

Did you know: Eden Krueger invented the Krueger sandwich to prove the safety of his new synthetic meat!
Displayed Text:
Vychodni potravinova krize

V roce 1976 stoupla hladina more na nejvyssi uroven od pocatku zaznamu. Zemekouli zachvatily zaplavy. Nasledna devastace infrastruktury vedla k rozsahlemu celosvetovemu nedostatku potravin a mnoha zemim hrozil hladomor. Ackoli UAS podala skromnou olivovou ratolest, k prekvapeni mnohych to byl zakladatel spolecnosti Starch Kola Eden Krueger, kdo poskytl nejvetsi pomoc. Krueger venoval na tento ucel obrovskou castku ze sveho osobniho majetku a financoval vyzkum syntetickych potravinovych nahrazek. V roce 1979 byla zverejnena technologie SynthMeat spolecnosti Starch Kola, cimz potravinova krize skoncila. 

Vedeli jste, ze: Eden Krueger vynalezl Kruegeruv sendvic, aby dokazal bezpecnost sveho noveho syntetickeho masa!

Notes:
The Mustard War

By 1891, the Anglo-French Empire was falling apart at the seams. Conflict and rebellions broke out across Europe. The Bourbon Court employed biological warfare in the form of mustard gas to quell the uprisings. By 1901, with millions of people suffering disfigurement and sickness thanks to the gas, and with the Anglo-French Empire's resources depleted, a cease-fire was called. 

Did you know: The Mustard War takes its name from the use of gas, as well as the Old Empire's heraldic colours!
Displayed Text:
Horcicna valka
V roce 1891 se anglo-francouzske imperium rozpadalo ve svech. Po cele Evrope propukaly konflikty a vzpoury. Bourbonsky dvur pouzil k potlaceni povstani biologickou valku v podobe yperitu. V roce 1901, kdy miliony lidi trpely znetvorenim a nemocemi zpusobenymi timto plynem a kdy byly zdroje anglo-francouzskeho imperia vycerpany, bylo vyhlaseno primeri. 

Vedeli jste, ze: Horcicna valka ziskala svuj nazev podle pouziti plynu a take podle heraldickych barev Stareho cisarstvi!

Notes: The Candor Book of World History Volume 2
Displayed Text: Kniha Candor o svetovych dejinach, svazek 2

Notes: The Unlucky Lottery\n\r\nIn an attempt to avoid large scale conflict and market destabilization, in 1904 the Eastern Dynasties launched a diversification directive which sent 1 in 5 people away to establish themselves on other continents. Although officially termed 'The Small Planet Directive' the scheme quickly became known as 'The Unlucky Lottery' due to its potential to split up families. Although highly controversial, it fulfilled the ED's goal in creating a more diverse global population. In 1960, however, the UAS introduced an offsetting scheme, allowing a person chosen by the lottery to send a volunteer in their place. Many émigrés took advantage and returned to their countries of origin, nullifying the directive's effectiveness and once again stoking tensions between east and west.
Displayed Text: Nestastna loterie\n\r\nVe snaze zabranit rozsahlym konfliktum a destabilizaci trhu zavedly vychodni dynastie v roce 1904 diverzifikacni smernici, v jejimz ramci se kazdy paty clovek vydal usadit se na jinych kontinentech. Ackoli se tento program oficialne nazyval 'smernice o malych planetach', rychle se mu zacalo rikat 'loterie nestesti', protoze mohl rozdelit rodiny. Ackoli byla velmi kontroverzni, splnila cil ED, kterym bylo vytvoreni rozmanitejsi globalni populace. V roce 1960 vsak UAS zavedla kompenzacni system, ktery umoznoval, aby osoba vybrana v loterii vyslala misto sebe dobrovolnika. Mnozi emigranti toho vyuzili a vratili se do zemi sveho puvodu, cimz se ucinnost smernice zmarila a opet se rozdmychalo napeti mezi Vychodem a Zapadem.

Notes: The Candor Book of World History Volume 3
Displayed Text: Kniha Candor o svetovych dejinach, svazek 3

Notes: The Titanic Disaster\r\n\r\nOn 15th April 1912, the UAS-owned airship Titanic mysteriously caught fire on her maiden flight over the North Atlantic. She crashed into the ocean, ultimately killing almost 2,000 people.
Displayed Text: Katastrofa Titaniku\r\n\r\n15. dubna 1912 zahadne vzplala vzducholod Titanik, vlastnena UAS, pri svem prvnim letu nad severnim Atlantikem. Zritila se do oceanu a nakonec zahynulo temer 2 000 lidi.

Notes: The Candor Book of World History Volume 4
Displayed Text: Kniha Candor o svetovych dejinach, svazek 4

Notes: The Candor Book of World History: Timeline
Displayed Text: Kniha Candor o svetovych dejinach: Casova osa

Notes: 1589: William Lee invents the first knitting machine. Queen Elizabeth I of England denies him a patent out of fear of making the hosier's guild obsolete. Lee moves to the continent and gains support of Henry IV 'Good King Henry' of France.
Displayed Text: 1589: William Lee vynalezne prvni pletaci stroj. Anglicka kralovna Alzbeta I. mu odmita udelit patent z obavy, ze by tim zastaral pletarsky cech. Lee se stehuje na kontinent a ziskava podporu francouzskeho krale Jindricha IV.

Notes: 1610: Lee's knitting machine sparks a glorious Industrial Revolution in Rouen, France.
Displayed Text: 1610: Leeho pletaci stroj zazehne ve francouzskem Rouenu slavnou prumyslovou revoluci.

Notes: 1656: Queen Nzinga seizes Luanda from the Portuguese. She goes on to form influential alliances and a trade consortium with many African countries.
Displayed Text: 1656: Kralovna Nzinga se zmocnuje Luandy od Portugalcu. Vytvari vlivna spojenectvi a obchodni konsorcia s mnoha africkymi zememi.

Notes: 1745: Thanks to increased French wealth and resources, a Jacobite Rebellion succeeds in conquering England. Bonnie Prince Charlie becomes Charles III, leading to long term peace with France.
Displayed Text: 1745: Diky rostoucimu francouzskemu bohatstvi a zdrojum se jakobitskemu povstani podari dobyt Anglii. Bonnie Prince Charlie se stava Karlem III., coz vede k dlouhodobemu miru s Francii.

Notes: 18th Century: England and France form a globally-dominant alliance, the Anglo-French Empire, ruled by Louis XVI and Marie Antoinette under the House of Bourbon
Displayed Text: 18. stoleti: Anglie a Francie vytvareji celosvetove dominantni alianci, anglo-francouzske imperium, kteremu vladnou Ludvik XVI. a Marie Antoinetta z rodu Bourbonu.

Notes: Seeing opportunity in the surge of wealth in Europe, rulers of China, Russia, Japan, parts of India and the Middle East form a powerful trade partnership known to the west as the Eastern Dynasties.
Displayed Text: Vladci Ciny, Ruska, Japonska, casti Indie a Blizkeho vychodu vidi prilezitost v prudkem rustu bohatstvi v Evrope a vytvareji mocne obchodni partnerstvi, ktere je na Zapade zname jako Vychodni dynastie.

Notes: 1775: In April, the Thirteen American Colonies create a Continental Army to capture Boston. However, they are outnumbered and outgunned by Anglo-French forces and in late 1776, the rebellion is crushed.
Displayed Text: 1775: V dubnu trinact americkych kolonii vytvari Kontinentalni armadu, ktera ma dobyt Boston. Anglo-francouzske sily je vsak precisluji a vyzbrojuji a koncem roku 1776 je povstani potlaceno.

Notes: 19th Century: Unable to rule over such vast distances and disparate peoples, the Anglo-French Empire begins to crumble. Many citizens turn against the Court, calling for localized democracy.
Displayed Text: 19. stoleti: Anglo-francouzske imperium se zacina rozpadat a neni schopno vladnout nad tak obrovskymi vzdalenostmi a rozdilnymi narody. Mnoho obcanu se obraci proti dvoru a pozaduje mistni demokracii.

Notes: 1879: Eden Krueger is born.
1891-1901: The Mustard War.
1900: Starch Kola founded by Eden Krueger. Originally sold as a tonic to soldiers to alleviate mustard sickness.
Displayed Text: 1900: Krueger zalozil firmu Starch Kola. Puvodne se prodaval jako tonikum pro vojaky na zmirneni horcicne nemoci.

Notes: 1901: The Anglo-French Empire is dismantled.
1902: The United Atlantic States forms in its place.
Displayed Text: 1902: Na jeho miste vznikaji Spojene staty atlanticke.

Notes: 1900s: Industrial pollution begins to cause climate change at an unprecedented rate. Many blame the use of bio-weapons.
Displayed Text: 1900s: Prumyslove znecisteni zacina zpusobovat nebyvalou zmenu klimatu. Mnozi z toho vini pouzivani biologickych zbrani.

Notes: 1904: The Small Planet Directive aka The Unlucky Lottery is launched.
Displayed Text: 1904: Je spustena smernice o male planete alias Smolna loterie.

Notes: 1909: In a bid to regenerate the western economy after the losses of the Mustard War, the UAS votes to give corporations the same rights as individuals
Displayed Text: 1909: Ve snaze obnovit zapadni ekonomiku po ztratach z horcicne valky odhlasuje UAS, ze korporace budou mit stejna prava jako jednotlivci.

Notes: 1910: The African Federation holds a summit to warn of the dangers of climate change.
Displayed Text: 1910: Africka federace porada summit, na kterem varuje pred nebezpecim zmeny klimatu.

Notes: 1912: The Titanic Disaster.
1919: The Vacuum Mail System is completed and approved for public use.
Displayed Text: 1919: Vakuovy postovni system je dokoncen a schvalen pro verejne pouziti.

Notes: 1924: Resistance to the Small Planet Directive grows among nationalist groups in the West. The UAS begins to rebuild its military in an attempt to compete with the East. A Cold War develops, leading to rapid advances in technology.
Displayed Text: 1924: Mezi nacionalistickymi skupinami na Zapade sili odpor proti smernici o male planete. UAS zacina obnovovat svou armadu ve snaze konkurovat Vychodu. Rozviji se studena valka, ktera vede k rychlemu technologickemu pokroku.

Notes: 1950: The first Cruncher is invented.
1955: Kaizen-6 Founder Kyra Cho is born.

Join me, Ren Ishida, on this journey to discover Kadō: The way of flowers.

When Kay Fernandez receives to a misdirected V-Mail containing a love letter, she is fascinated by the author and their beautiful writing. Against her better judgement, she replies, and finds herself in correspondence with a mysterious suitor, who signs themselves only 'Z'. But as feelings grow, so too does the danger; Z works for a rival corporation, and their love could ruin both their lives. Will the star-crossed lovers risk everything to be together?
Displayed Text: ZNAMY ROMAN ZAKAZANY VICE NEZ DVACET LET\n\nKdyz Kay Fernandezova obdrzi nespravne nasmerovany V-Mail obsahujici milostny dopis, je fascinovana autorem a jeho krasnym pismem. Navzdory svemu rozumu odpovi a ocitne se v korespondenci se zahadnym napadnikem, ktery se podepisuje pouze 'Z'. S rostoucimi city vsak roste i nebezpeci; Z pracuje pro konkurencni korporaci a jejich laska by mohla obema znicit zivot. Budou hvezdni milenci riskovat vse, aby mohli byt spolu?
