Notes: A Blue Star for Uncle
Falstaff's Locusts

Jen Block, a failing playwright wakes to find her apartment swarming with locusts. She follows them to their source: a volume of The Complete Works of Shakespeare on her bookcase, where she discovers that each page is a conduit to a frightening, alternate reality...\n\n'A mesmerizing trip and a late masterpiece from this mercurial genius.' – Hamane Lyon
Displayed Text: Jen Blockova, neuspesna dramaticka, se probudi a zjisti, ze se jeji byt hemzi kobylkami. Vyda se za nimi az k jejich zdroji: svazku Shakespearova dila, ktery lezi na jeji knihovne, a zjisti, ze kazda stranka je pruchodem do desive alternativni reality... \n\n'Fascinujici vylet a pozdni mistrovske dilo tohoto rtutoviteho genia.' - Hamane Lyon

Notes: Kolob Grieving

Ten years after leaving Earth, as the solo engineer of the first astro V-Mail pipe, Kolob King waits alone on a satellite station for the message that will announce the first wave of settlers are on their way. However, when a message finally arrives, it is not a greeting but a random page from novel, seemingly about his own life. As more pages arrive, out of sync, Kolob begins to wonder what is left on the other end of the tube...
Displayed Text: Deset let po opusteni Zeme ceka Kolob King jako samostatny inzenyr prvniho astro V-Mailu sam na satelitni stanici na zpravu, ktera oznami, ze prvni vlna osadniku je na ceste. Kdyz vsak zprava konecne dorazi, neni to pozdrav, ale nahodna stranka z romanu, zdanlive o jeho vlastnim zivote. Jak prichazeji dalsi stranky, ktere nejsou synchronizovane, Kolob zacina premyslet, co zustalo na druhem konci trubice...

Notes: Luna Venture
The Eyes of Carrington Lux

Carrington Lux is a astro-navigator aboard the KCS Atarashī, plotting a course to the Planet E01: the new home of humanity. One day Lux wakes to find the ship lost in deep space. After a terrifying few months of drifting, they find themselves back where they started, above Earth. However, everything seems different, and Lux can't shake the feeling that this Earth is not the one they left...
Displayed Text: Carrington Lux je astronavigator na palube lodi KCS Atarashi, ktery planuje kurz k planete E01: novemu domovu lidstva. Jednoho dne se Lux probudi a zjisti, ze se lod ztratila v hlubokem vesmiru. Po nekolika desivych mesicich driftovani se ocitnou tam, kde zacali, nad Zemi. Vsechno se vsak zda byt jinak a Lux se nemuze zbavit pocitu, ze tahle Zeme neni ta, kterou opustili...

FINAL NOTICE\nOPEN IMMEDIATELY

Welcome tenant,

It ain't much, but it's better than sleeping rough. |city.name| is a cruel place, but this apartment is my attempt at offering some solace.

Notes:
If you need cash, check out the notice boards next to public telephones in bars and restaurants for jobs.

Keep an eye out for murder cases. They carry a hefty bounty and Enforcers ain't interested in dirtying their hands with detective work. Best money we can get right now.

Jobs will get you social credit as well as cash, enough and you can officially retire to The Fields. We can only dream.

-|story.flophouseowner.initial|
Displayed Text:
Pokud potrebujete hotovost, podivejte se na nastenky vedle verejnych telefonu v barech a restauracich, kde najdete nabidky prace.

Sledujte pripady vrazd. Za ne se vyplaci vysoka odmena a vymahaci si nechteji spinit ruce detektivni praci. Nejlepsi penize, ktere ted muzeme dostat.

Prace vam prinese socialni kredit i penize, staci a muzete oficialne odejit do duchodu do Poli. O tom si muzeme nechat jenom zdat.

-|story.flophouseowner.initial|

Notes: New Block
When breaking into a room, it's a good idea to check for cameras. If you are worried about them you can turn them off by using the security breaker box connected to the camera.
Displayed Text: Pri vloupani do mistnosti je dobre zkontrolovat, zda v ni nejsou kamery. Pokud se jich obavate, muzete je vypnout pomoci bezpecnostni vypinaci skrinky pripojene ke kamere.

Notes: In residential properties, it's worth checking under the doormat for a key!
Displayed Text: V obytnych domech se vyplati podivat se pod rohozku, zda tam neni klic!

Notes: Most rooms will feature some kind of ventilation system, when struggling to find a safe entrance this could be a great way in!
Displayed Text: Vetsina mistnosti je vybavena nejakym vetracim systemem, ktery muze byt skvelou moznosti, jak se dostat dovnitr, kdyz se snazite najit bezpecny vchod!

Notes: If in a rush, or out of other options, you can also break down the door. This might take several attempts and is very noisy.
Displayed Text: Pokud spechate nebo nemate jine moznosti, muzete dvere take vyrazit. To muze trvat nekolik pokusu a je to velmi hlucne.

Notes: Commercial properties often contain a wealth of information in privately accessed rooms. Usually to access this you'll need to find a key code for the door.
Displayed Text: Komercni nemovitosti casto obsahuji mnozstvi informaci v soukromych mistnostech. Pro pristup k nim je obvykle treba najit kod ke dverim.

Notes: You may be able to find it hidden around on a note.
Displayed Text: Mozna ji najdete schovanou na poznamce.

Notes: Your other options are to bribe the staff, or use a device called a 'codebreaker', which you can purchase from the vending machines at City Hall.
Displayed Text: Dalsi moznosti je podplatit zamestnance nebo pouzit zarizeni zvane 'koder', ktere si muzete zakoupit v automatech na radnici.

Notes: You will not be allowed in this room, so make your approach stealthy and avoid or disable security systems by using the breaker box.
Displayed Text: Do teto mistnosti nebudete vpusteni, takze se k ni priblizujte nenapadne a vyhnete se bezpecnostnim systemum nebo je vyradte pomoci vypinace.

Notes: You can trace the red wires from security systems to find these boxes. They will themselves require lock-picking.
Displayed Text: Tyto skrinky muzete najit po cervenych vodicich od bezpecnostnich systemu. Samy o sobe budou vyzadovat vylomeni zamku.

Notes: Point the scanner where you want to scan. Almost all surfaces can contain fingerprints.
Displayed Text: Nasmerujte skener tam, kde chcete skenovat. Temer vsechny povrchy mohou obsahovat otisky prstu.

Notes: Setting the watch alarm will dictate how long you wait for. You can also cancel by getting out of the seat or bed.
Displayed Text: Nastavenim budiku hodinek urcite, jak dlouho budete cekat. Budik muzete zrusit take tim, ze vstanete ze sedacky nebo postele.

Notes: So just as you may want to be careful about entering, it's often a good idea to identify means to help you make a safe escape...
Displayed Text: Stejne jako si muzete davat pozor pri vstupu, je casto dobre urcit si prostredky, ktere vam pomohou bezpecne uniknout...

Notes: Keep an eye out for air ducts you can escape to in a hurry...

Notes: Once you've figured out the culprit, you may want to perform a citizen's arrest. To do this you'll need handcuffs; you can find them at the vending machines at City Hall.

Notes: Once arrested, citizens are much more likely to answer your questions. After about two hours, any handcuffed citizens that are not reported as part of a case submission will be freed. You'll also need to acquire their name for the case form objective to recognise that you've completed the arrest objective.

Budete take muset ziskat jejich jmeno pro cil formulare pripadu, aby bylo rozpoznano, ze jste splnili cil zatceni.

Chtel jsem ti jen poslat kratky V-mail, abych ti dal vedet, ze jsem na tvou letosni praci velmi pysny! Vsichni jste se toho tolik naucili a snazili jste se, jak nejlepe dovedete, a to i pres vsechny nase bezpecnostni incidenty!

Napadlo me, ze bych mohl napsat kratkou poznamku o profesnich normach. Aby bylo jasno, ocekava se, ze prijdete vcas, bez stiznosti a pripraveni pracovat. Rad bych videl mene pomluv, mene place a rozhodne mene krysich chlupu na obleceni. Uf! Trochu hrdosti, prosim!\r\n

Vsiml jsem si, ze jsi 8., 13., 21. a 29. minuleho mesice volal, ze jsi nemocny. Nemohu si nevsimnout, ze presne odpovidaly domacim zapasum Starch Kola Sugarbirds. Od teto chvile sleduji rozvrh a ty jsi v pozoru.

Hadejte co? Konecne odtud odchazim! Uz jen standardni desetimesicni vypovedni lhuta a pak jdu pryc! Doufam, ze i vy budete moci brzy odejit! Tohle je nejhorsi misto na svete a nejhorsi firma na svete! Uz se nikdy nevratim! \r

Vsiml jsem si, ze jste pozadal o pomerne vyrazne zvyseni platu: 5%! Pani! To je zajimave cislo. Pojdme se sejit a probrat, jak si ho muzete zaslouzit! Treba prevzeti uklidovych praci? Pokud nemate jine navrhy!

Nepreji si, aby se opakoval lonsky debakl. Ucast na Candor Party je povinna a my budeme kontrolovat jmena na vyplatnich paskach, abychom se ujistili, ze jste pritomni. Ocekavame, ze se budete dobre bavit. \r

Pripominame, ze pristi tyden se kona vecere ke Dni zakladatelu El-Gen! Jsem si jisty, ze letos nechceme videt zadne flakace Samse nebo asocialni Alenky! Stoprocentni ucast je nutna. Tesime se, az vas tam uvidime!\r\nVelke objeti!

Zase je tu ta cast roku! Nemuzeme se dockat, az se zitra uvidime na Kensington Indigo Party. Pripominame, ze ucast je povinna a standardnim trestem je okamzite ukonceni pracovniho pomeru! A nezapomente se obleknout!

Blizi se mesicni obchodni snidane Starch Kola. Vsichni zamestnanci se ji musi zucastnit. Obdrzite jednu (1) vafli, jednu (1) Sauxsage (TM) a jednu (1) plechovku Starch. Na jidlo a zhodnoceni budete mit tricet minut.
Proste to vylozim. Ano, videl jsem, ze jsme se vcera vecer shodli na Dove. Ano, myslim, ze je to chyba v cruncheru. Proste... uz se o tom nikdy nezminujme, ano? Zejmena ty obrazky.
Nevidel jsi NIC, jasny? NIKDY jsme se neshodli na Dove a ja jsem... v inzeratu neuvedl... zadne konkretni PREFERENCE, kdybychom se shodli. Nebo ne?

Pravdepodobne to vypada podobne, jako kdyz jsme se drive shodli na Dove! Myslim, ze se opravdu stalo to, ze hodne lidi ma jmeno jako ja. A obrazek jako ja! Naprosto pochopitelna chyba. Kazdopadne se tesim, ze uz se o tom nikdy nezminim! Nikdy!
Pripominame, ze trubice V-mailu se maji pouzivat pouze pro V-mail a ze neustalym vkladanim svacin do trubic riskujeme poskozeni systemu, nemluve o viru cruncher. Okamzite s tim prestante.

Jen kratka poznamka, abych rekl, ze bych byl rad, kdyby lide trochu zpomalili nebo dokonce prestali davat veci do V-mailovych trubek! Za poslednich par tydnu jsem musel vybilit mrtve mysi, klice od domu, sladkosti a par dost kompromitujicich fotek! Predem dekuji! Omlouvam se, ze jsem tak prisny!
Laskave prestante do trubek davat cokoli krome posty V. Nas uklidovy personal ma potize s neustalym odstranovanim vaseho obleceni. Navic, co je s vami?
